      Description

      The Boston Celtics are an American professional basketball team based in Boston. The Celtics compete in the National Basketball Association as a member of the Atlantic Division of the Eastern Conference. Wikipedia
      Head coach: Joe Mazzulla
      Arena/Stadium: TD Garden
      Founder: Walter A. Brown
      Founded: June 6, 1946
      Headquarters: Boston, Massachusetts, United States
      President: Rich Gotham
